1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根据所包含地震的区域范围，地震目录可以分成两类：全球地震目录和区域地震目录。\n顾名思义，全球地震目录包含了全球范围内的地震，但通常只包含比较大的地震，小地震多有遗漏；\n区域地震目录则只关注某个特定区域内的地震，通常包含更多的小地震。","position":{"start":{"line":104,"column":1},"end":{"line":104,"column":1}},"key":"ww4VU09zcL"}],"key":"sDyRJKnk7f"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":108,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"常见的全球地震目录包括：","position":{"start":{"line":108,"column":1},"end":{"line":108,"column":1}},"key":"HTN4c4BPeD"}],"key":"n7zH5c9zjn"},{"type":"definitionList","position":{"start":{"line":110,"column":1},"end":{"line":120,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"definitionTerm","position":{"start":{"line":110,"column":1},"end":{"line":109,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"link","url":"http://www.isc.ac.uk/iscbulletin/","position":{"start":{"line":110,"column":1},"end":{"line":110,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"International Seismological Center 地震目录","position":{"start":{"line":110,"column":1},"end":{"line":110,"column":1}},"key":"KSl89TVRyI"}],"urlSource":"http://www.isc.ac.uk/iscbulletin/","key":"T0CjTPs0eb"}],"key":"CzWIuJQJn0"},{"type":"definitionDescription","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":114,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ISC 地震目录是全球地震的最终版本，涵盖了\n1900 年至今的地震信息。所有地震信息通过程序自动确定，并由 ISC 的分析人员对其\n进行人工检查和重定位。经过人工审核的 ISC 地震目录通常有 24 个月的延迟。","position":{"start":{"line":111,"column":1},"end":{"line":111,"column":1}},"key":"w70RfjowGr"}],"key":"ut3pCkZKsB"},{"type":"definitionTerm","position":{"start":{"line":115,"column":1},"end":{"line":114,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"link","url":"https://earthquake.usgs.gov/data/comcat/","position":{"start":{"line":115,"column":1},"end":{"line":115,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ANSS ComCat 地震目录","position":{"start":{"line":115,"column":1},"end":{"line":115,"column":1}},"key":"UUkvV3eyvf"}],"urlSource":"https://earthquake.usgs.gov/data/comcat/","key":"AEBzwpFIEu"}